               <head>Foundation of hospital; Ipswich; 4 Elizabeth (1561-1562)</head>
               <msContents>
                  <textLang mainLang="en">English</textLang>
                  <msItem>
                     <p> Indenture made <origDate when="1562-07-16">16 July, 4 Elizabeth (1562)</origDate><!--1561-11-17|1562-11-16-->, reciting the bequest of
                  <persName>
                           <forename>Henry</forename> 
                           <surname>Tooley</surname></persName>, and the surrender to the 
                  <orgName key="org_105036">mayor and corporation of <pb n="487"/> Ipswich</orgName>, of the lands, &amp;c. given for the
                  foundation of an <orgName key="org_105031">hospital at Ipswich</orgName>. 
                  [3.5 sheets; mutilated.]
                  
                  </p>
